          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is used for consultation and study and is an astrological text used by a priest or householder for the purpose of divining future events that will effect specific details of a person's life; contains discussions of planetary movements and agricultural themes, includes a diagram of a serpent with asterism within its body (f. 20v); also contains tables and charts containing Sanskrit syllables and numbers. Manuscript is incomplete and may have combined parts of two different manuscripts.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Śīghrabodha</title>
              <title type="vernacular">शीघ्रबोध</title>
